ads.heading: Improve your Hindi Handwriting
ads.description:
We have 24 sessions course divided amongst 2 levels of 12 sessions each-

Basic 12 sessions' focus points are- 
1. Improving the structuring of individual स्वर and व्यंजन while making use of loops and strokes
2. Joining of शब्द with मात्रा 
3. Speed Techniques Incorporation with मात्रा while practicing वाक्य, अनुच्छेद 

Advance 12 sessions' focus areas are-
1. परीक्षा की तैयारी (margins, spacing & alignment)
2. विराम चिन्ह और अंक 
3. वाक्य, अनुच्छेद लेखन  practice with speed 
4. Handwriting Competition
